'''Ramón Pérez''' is an artist most famous for his illustrations of the [[Jensaarai/Legends|Jensaarai]] sect of [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force users]] for ''[[Polyhedron]]''. He has also also provided artwork for several issues of ''[[Star Wars Gamer]]'' magazine.

